  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To test the efﬁcacy of 14 day levoﬂoxacin and bismuth-containing second-line therapy for
      resistant Helicobacter pylori infection, to compare with the classical quadruple therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
